"First of all, non ritual compliments a&nbsp;@PastorellaGiu&nbsp; for the result obtained with a courageous congressional battle. Thanks to all the militants and candidates who have spent themselves. Making congresses is a complicated but necessary exercise. Now at work together to grow the party," wrote Calenda on social media.
